snippet: An antitrust lawsuit targeting Google's Android operating system should be dismissed, Google said in a court filing on Friday, partly because smartphone manufacturers are free to utilize Android on their phones without also installing Google apps....

headline.print_headline: Google Seeks to Dismiss U.S. Antitrust Lawsuit Over Android
headline.main: Google Seeks to Dismiss U.S. Antitrust Lawsuit Over Android

lead_paragraph: An antitrust lawsuit targeting Google's Android operating system should be dismissed, Google said in a court filing on Friday, partly because smartphone manufacturers are free to utilize Android on their phones without also installing Google apps.
